window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>They had seven years to prepare. Earth is lost. </p> <p>Seven years ago the New Earth colony received one final message from Earth...a warning. First a global pandemic, then the emergence of a new species. A war for survival ravaged the Sol system. Now they are coming for the colony. </p> <p>Many colonists don't believe it, but Connor does. They must prepare. They must fight. But how can they survive something that killed every person back on Earth? </p>"; 
